// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4775 — Mass File Rename (ransomhub)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 797c2699-9479-5687-add2-2818106f2e75

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
